## Git branches (read this first)

| Branch | Role |
|--------|------|
| **`beta/beta`** | **Primary branch** — this is the integration line that **pack-attack.de** deploys from. Treat it as “main” for day-to-day work. |
| **`main`** | **Separate branch** — not auto-deployed. Keep it only if you use it for releases, snapshots, or GitHub default; it does **not** have to match `beta/beta`. |

**Do not merge `beta/beta` into `main` just to “sync” unless you explicitly want that.** Production follows **`beta/beta`** only (see `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`).

