## Deployment

### Quick Deploy (from local machine)
```powershell
ssh -i "$env:USERPROFILE\.ssh\packattack-server" root@82.165.66.236 "cd /var/www/packattack/app && git fetch origin beta/beta && git reset --hard origin/beta/beta && npm ci && npx prisma generate && npm run build && npx prisma migrate deploy && pm2 reload packattack --update-env && pm2 status"
```

### On-Server Deploy
```bash
cd /var/www/packattack/app
sudo -u packattack git fetch origin beta/beta
sudo -u packattack git reset --hard origin/beta/beta
sudo -u packattack npm ci --production=false
sudo -u packattack npx prisma generate
sudo -u packattack npx prisma migrate deploy
sudo -u packattack npm run build
sudo -u packattack pm2 reload packattack --update-env
```

### Health Check
```bash
curl https://pack-attack.de/api/health
```

